Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.11,0:00:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}像鲜红的夜一般遮蔽了黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.47,0:00:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}亲爱的 你可以藏起你的恐惧 也可以自欺欺人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}就这样徜徉于梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}展开鲜血淋漓的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}什么是谎言？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}什么是真相？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}又该相信什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}像堕落的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}随着时代的风 随波逐流 堕落覆灭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}朝着繁星密布的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.15,0:01:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}像女神一般 拥抱着永远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.43,0:01:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}向天堂展翅翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.52,0:22:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}大地与天空 究竟为何分离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.91,0:22:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}世界如此残酷 却又如此美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}投掷石块者 与遭投掷者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}两者被难以逾越的 栅栏阻隔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}若是转变立场 正义将龇露獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}在牢笼中咆哮的 究竟是哪一方？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:23:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}献出心脏 为回不去的黄昏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}前行不止的长夜尽头 乐园位于何方…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.72,0:23:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}安魂曲（Requiem） 安魂曲（Requiem）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.92,0:23:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}在此夜凋零的无名之花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}请于拂晓之时安息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}旁观者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}等等…站住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}总觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}跟想像中的女王不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.49,0:01:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}戴上王冠是两个月前的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}现在反而比较像是孤儿院的院长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你们知道她在城里被说成什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我不是说了点心要等帮忙工作之后吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}说她是“放牛女神”呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真是的，贪吃鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当然也是带着亲近的含义啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}结果还是成了神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这样谁都不会记得把托洛斯特区的洞补上的家伙了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.06,0:02:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}希斯特利亚之所以决定成为女王的其中一个理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就是为了做这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这件事是指
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.06,0:02:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}把地下街区聚集的孤儿和穷人一同照料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}地下街区出身的兵长似乎也力挺这个提案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}她说过如果有感到困扰的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不管人在哪都会找出来并帮助他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}原来这就是希丝特莉亚想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}又在偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}再拖下去就要天黑了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那家伙好像越来越像我老妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}女神大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}硬质化实验似乎进行得很顺利嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不过得抓紧时间才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们又会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你想怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果再度见到莱纳和贝尔托特的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我就得…杀了他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}要是能快点知道就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}知道这世界到底为什么会变成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为现实不容我们后悔自己做过的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}最近从地下街区来的孩子们也变得会笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这怎么会是错的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.28,0:03:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}明明说了人类什么的干脆灭亡算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那 那只是我一时气头上乱说的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连做实验已经很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}说的也是 对不起 三笠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}别把我当老人对待行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}虽因兵团的肃请使人类中枢失去许多人才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但也获得了诸如在地下空间发现发光矿石等成果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}而艾连的硬质化能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也催生出一种对抗巨人专用的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}再把头伸进来一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:05:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}打中后颈了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}下次一定可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}成功了 打败12米级巨人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这样就算不派出士兵作战 也能打倒巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}能全天候连续运转砍伐巨人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}地狱处刑者诞生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}做得好 艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}大概是因为过度使用巨人之力了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}毕竟最近一直都在做硬质化的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}抱歉 艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}请不要道歉 汉吉队长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我累了又怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}让我们快点在希干希纳区备齐武器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}能赢 这样能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只要有新兵器 巨人就跟纸屑一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真是的 兴奋个什么劲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是吹了什么风 现在才跑来当什么调查兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就是啊 没被希琪阻止吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}希琪 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还说为什么 因为你们两个不是…那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不太懂你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不过希琪一直骂我说不适合 根本就是找死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}最后还说什么继续待在宪兵团里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就能获得很多好处之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}亏我还对她有所改观
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所以我骂了她一句“真是看错你了”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}吃屎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}马洛你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这家伙是混蛋河童呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}干嘛啦 马洛又没说错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}总之还能嘻嘻哈哈的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}都是跟你一样 没有实战经验被发配过来的人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}想说你们已经是身经百战的猛将吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}跟你们比起来的话算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真过分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不都同为104期兵嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}而且可不是只有我们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:07:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}墙里可全都因为“夺回玛利亚之墙”而在兴头上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不过 你们的确变了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}该说是神情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}到底发生过什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不 还是下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那我先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}已经要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}明天是调整日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所以我打算早上回我村里一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}说不定还能知道些什么 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}让柯尼的妈妈恢复原状的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}并不是完全不存在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}接下来继续进行巨人的研究的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}巨人的真实身份是人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只是有这个可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}差不多60年左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}像是做着一个永远不会醒的恶梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}恶梦吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}发生了那么多事一直没办法细想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但我们一直在与之战斗的敌人到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也就是说 所谓的巨人其实是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不停被噩梦缠身的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我也曾经一时变成那样的巨人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你面包和汤还没吃完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}聊天等吃完饭再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}抱歉 三笠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真是够了 艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你最近老是这样耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一个人喃喃自语的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:09:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你该想起来的应该是“那个男人”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你不是看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在洞窟被强迫回溯记忆的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那个跟你老爸见面的调查军团的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在那天那种状况下跟老爸见面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他肯定知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}说起来那个男人我也肯定在哪见过才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不是叶卡医生的记忆 而是艾连的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我是这么觉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不然找个地方撞头看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就是啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}居然整天嚷嚷说是为了回想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一直抓着希丝特莉亚的手不放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真该赏你个教官的头槌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果那样就能想起来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}训练兵团教官 奇斯·夏迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他是在艾尔文之前的第12代团长哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们也很久没见到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}夏迪斯教官…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}现在可以公开的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}地狱处刑人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连叶卡成功操纵硬质化能力后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}将其与墙壁结合构筑而成的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}半自动式巨人驱逐兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}能以比至今都更加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}安全的方式讨伐巨人将其驱逐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}怎么了 布劳斯 不坐下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不必了 我站这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}的确 你当时经常被叫来这教官室狠训呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}从那之后才过没几个月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}大家都变得让我快认不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}夏迪斯团长…不 教官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}相信您已经察觉正准备实施玛利亚之墙夺回作战的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}此刻前来叨扰的理由了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连 你长得真像你母亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但寄宿在那双眼眸中的利牙 就跟你父亲一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}请告诉我你知道的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我什么都不知道 如果要从结论而言的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但如果愿意听点对人类毫无利益可言的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我就讲讲只能称得上是旁观者的 自己的往事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}20年前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他出现在玛利亚之墙 希干希纳区大门前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:12:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你在这做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你是怎么越过城墙的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你 你们才是 在墙外做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}难道说 是在战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也不知道是真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他完全不记得自己为何会在墙外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当时的他失去了所有的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只记得自己的名字叫做古利夏·叶卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}想不到还有严禁擅自踏入巨人领域之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}明明会特地跑到墙壁外晃荡的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}除了你们调查军团以外根本没别人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}难道没有哪条法律能把在勤务中喝酒的笨蛋塞进牢里吗 汉尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}总之也没出现被害者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就别跟上头报告了 行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你打算回哪去 古利夏·叶卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}除了名字我还记得一件事 我是个医生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}请帮我介绍医院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}应该有我能做的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后 能告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}关于这个世界的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还有关于调查军团…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}关于你们的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他是真的一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}关于这个世界的事情 什么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}虽然是有贫富差距
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但在墙里还算和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}至少并不需要畏惧着巨人而活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.63,0:13:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}“太好了”吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你也这么觉得吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}看样子你是个在这狭窄墙内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只要有饭有酒就能满足的那类人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}想都没想过世界究竟有多宽广
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你去到墙外的理由是因为那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那就是调查军团
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是啊…觉得我们很笨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你们比这墙里的任何人都还要聪明勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你们的存在就代表了灵魂的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是人类的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}骄傲…我们吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}等等 奇斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}又在拉人进调查军团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不 不是啦卡露拉 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那不是我这种人能担负得起的职务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}调查军团应该得是更特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}被上天选中的人才适合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}天选之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我还是第一次被人这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}的确墙壁中的世界对我来说太狭窄了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}又是重大损害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}墙外据点到底何时才能建成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只要我能当上团长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就能做出成果来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只要展现凡人那微小容量的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也能理解的丰功伟业
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}大家就会认同我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}古利夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}卡露拉也感染了流行性传染病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}能想点办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}带到后面的床铺去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}叶卡医生…我的父母也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没问题 大家都能得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}叶卡医生 我太太能起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}叶卡医生 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}任命你成为调查军团团长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}恭喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}恭喜 叶卡医生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可恶 据点被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不行了我们撒退吧 团长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那个只懂得突击的无脑团长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就他自己又一个人死里逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但是听说艾尔文的小队现在还没死过人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}干脆换个团长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}特别的…天选之人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}奇斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}卡露拉 这孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连 是男孩唷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.55,0:17:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}信果然没寄到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我先生也很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.85,0:17:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这种事…你打算一直做到死为止吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}别再做这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你知道为何凡人能庸碌苟活至死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}首要就是因为缺乏想像力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所以完全不以毫无成就 只会吃喝拉撒的人生为耻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.63,0:18:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}成就丰功伟业…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不 就连要理解也是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}连其一丝端倪都无法认知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}随意对男人摇头摆尾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只会倒酒端盘没有其他长处的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}绝对…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}凡人无法成就任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾尔文 你愿意当团长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有生来特别的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只是那不是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这么简单的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我那时为什么没意识到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}玛利亚之墙被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}希干希纳区似乎被破坏殆尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}托洛斯特区这也很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}奇斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是你呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}快起来 艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}妈妈没跟你在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}老爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}妈妈被巨人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}吃掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连 你要替妈妈报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你一定做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}等等 你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}请不要跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你来替卡露拉报仇不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为你是特别的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}跟我不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这孩子应该也不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他说不定不是天选之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你又要对人施加诅咒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这孩子跟你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}拜托了 请不要干涉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}打雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:21:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}然后我把昏倒的你带回避难所的床铺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这就是我所知的全部了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只有这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.37,0:21:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我知道您退任的真正理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}并不是对死去部下的赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}而是因为察觉到自己并非特别什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为如此幼稚的理由躲到这来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}别说了 汉吉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我完全不在乎你抱着怎样的自卑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不要逃避现实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.97,0:21:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}对公众献出心脏不就是这么回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}请别说了 汉吉队长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就跟教官说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我一点都不特别
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只不过是那个特别的父亲的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就只是这样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.04,0:22:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你的母亲…卡露拉曾这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.04,0:22:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不是特别的就不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.63,0:22:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我不这么认为哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}至少这孩子…才不需要变得多伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.35,0:22:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就算没有比别人优越…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.35,0:22:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为你看 他多可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.99,0:22:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所以这孩子已经很伟大了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}毕竟他可是出生到这世上了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你应该会像你父亲期望的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}燃烧自己的生命 在墙外化为灰烬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.52,0:23:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我只是一介什么也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.69,0:23:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}什么也改变不了的…旁观者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.47,0:23:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}出发前往希干希纳区的前一天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.18,0:23:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}知晓了墙外世界的存在的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.52,0:23:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}怀抱着疑惑与期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.69,0:23:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}为人类的将来祈梼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.68,0:23:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}下一回“夺还作战的夜晚”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.52,0:22:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}大地と大空は 何故別れたのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.91,0:22:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}世界は残酷で されど美しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}石を投げる者と 投げられる者には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}容易に越えられぬ 柵がある
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}立ち位置が替われば 正義は牙を剥く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}檻の中で吼えているのは 果たしてどちらか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:23:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}心臓を捧げた 戻せない黄昏に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}進み続けた夜の果て 楽園は何処にある？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.72,0:23:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}Requiem Requiem
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.92,0:23:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}この夜に散った名も無き花よ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\an8\1c&H0080FF&\i1}どうか安らかに暁に眠れ

